{"tid":2333934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎｜變種毒株「失控」傳遍英國 意大利荷蘭丹麥澳洲有病例 歐洲多國禁英航班入境","createTime":"2020-12-20T21:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T21:15:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27232026889284c3b04dc382a8f15dffa32a876b","tid":2333934,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T21:15:49.000Z","msg":"【新增法國德國禁英國航班】英國公共衞生部傳染病顧問霍普金斯（Susan Hopkins）周日向英國天空新聞表示，新種武漢肺炎病毒株已經傳遍英國，惟個案遠少於倫敦、肯特郡及埃塞克斯部分地區，連威爾斯、蘇格蘭都有病例，只是北愛未有。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201221/PSZAZYNXHRHBTGYCIJXB53YJGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201221%2FPSZAZYNXHRHBTGYCIJXB53YJGQ%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=0afa8d77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201221%2FPSZAZYNXHRHBTGYCIJXB53YJGQ%2F&h=79030add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201221/PSZAZYNXHRHBTGYCIJXB53YJGQ/</a>"}]}